{"tid":1739383,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"RTHK 獨裁者攻略","createTime":"2019-11-19T14:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T23:59:46.000Z","uid":228555,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"523692389ce699bf9058f01457464bd05c471a79","tid":1739383,"uid":228555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:35:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/thedictatorsplaybook/episode/603990\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fthedictatorsplaybook%2Fepisode%2F603990&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqBPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=62aa615c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/thedictatorsplaybook/episode/603990</a><br />\n金日成是一位傳奇的游擊隊戰士，在1930年代積極參與抗戰，使朝鮮擺脫日本的佔領。他隨後發動朝鮮戰爭，並建立了朝鮮民主主義人民共和國，亦是世界上控監管最嚴密的國家。究竟金日成是如何穩操勝算，取得大權，將自己化身成如神祇般的領導人，並延伸至今長達三代人的獨裁統治？<br />\n在此紀錄片系列所提及的獨裁者之中，金日成可算是影響力最持久的一位。他所塑造的國家仍然處於極權主義制度之下，估計約有10萬人被囚禁在勞改營中。自1950年代北韓確定以獨裁統治國家後，國民對金氏家族的崇拜在往後的70年後依然沒有絲毫改變。今天，北韓是由他的孫兒金正恩統治，他也如神祇般被國民所膜拜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共完全複製緊北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40ad44c053fecca368c9b21e97df72efc01c0d8","tid":1739383,"uid":22822,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:37:03.000Z","msg":"好好睇，同而家習維尼好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009272272f7fa7788c3096c4532baa38e01444b9","tid":1739383,"uid":228555,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c40ad44c053fecca368c9b21e97df72efc01c0d8","tid":1739383,"uid":22822,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:37:03.000Z","msg":"好好睇，同而家習維尼好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:40:02.000Z","msg":"根本做緊同一樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10e05b2d00e4648160c29c8da6027d848877a5c","tid":1739383,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:00:20.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"e82ae2cb4c2770076971efc9acbdfec040bbbcbc","tid":1739383,"uid":251775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:26:04.000Z","msg":"睇完<br />\n美國當年最撚失敗就係空襲完冇順勢統一埋北韓 而家留撚左勁大個毒瘤俾自己同埋全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c375d08a02948c6554cf58d3ee58df278f39d3dc","tid":1739383,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:46:23.000Z","msg":"好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee237cc4e09acf5f742b80578e61aa3f51978b8","tid":1739383,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e82ae2cb4c2770076971efc9acbdfec040bbbcbc","tid":1739383,"uid":251775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:26:04.000Z","msg":"睇完<br />\n美國當年最撚失敗就係空襲完冇順勢統一埋北韓 而家留撚左勁大個毒瘤俾自己同埋全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:58:52.000Z","msg":"我諗美國當時根本唔想兩韓統一？<br />\n因為就咁睇條片<br />\n金日成攻打南韓似乎係得到人民支持<br />\n加上美國一次過炸死左北韓兩成人<br />\n就算美國幫南韓佔領北韓<br />\n根本管治唔到北韓的人民 基乎肯定會進入內亂／內戰狀態<br />\n對南韓／美國都唔會有好處<br />\n當時美國需要一個東亞基地抗衡中共同蘇聯<br />\n美國的策略應該係叫北韓退返落三八線 自己搞掂自己<br />\n然後穩定南韓做戰略基地就算？<br />\n南韓對於制衡中國同蘇聯黎講應該算係一個幾重要的戰略基地"},{"pid":"75a6ec55f178d961f4849c99d87f58b1a99af641","tid":1739383,"uid":158355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e82ae2cb4c2770076971efc9acbdfec040bbbcbc","tid":1739383,"uid":251775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:26:04.000Z","msg":"睇完<br />\n美國當年最撚失敗就係空襲完冇順勢統一埋北韓 而家留撚左勁大個毒瘤俾自己同埋全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T18:19:22.000Z","msg":"美國當年最撚成功就係知道